                                SUBSTRING('00', 1, 2 - LEN(CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(HOUR, "OraSfarsit")))) + CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(HOUR, "OraSfarsit")) + ':' +
                                SUBSTRING('00', 1, 2 - LEN(CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraSfarsit")))) + CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraSfarsit")) + '; ' ELSE '' END
                                AS "DateConcatenate", DR."Valoare" AS Anulare_Valoare, DR."NrZile" AS Anulare_NrZile, COALESCE(A."CampBifa",0) AS "CampBifa"
                                FROM (SELECT A.*, 0 AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN (A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) OR B."IdCerere" IS NULL) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" = 2 AND B."IdStare" IN (1, 2, 3, 4)
                                WHERE A.F10003 = -99
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, CASE WHEN C."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN C."Id" ELSE (CASE WHEN B."IdSuper" > 0 THEN 76 ELSE C."Id" END) END AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN (A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."IdUser" = 2
                                LEFT JOIN "tblSupervizori" C ON (-1 * B."IdSuper")= C."Id"     --AND COALESCE(C."ModululCereriAbsente", 0) = 1
                                WHERE A.F10003 <> -99 
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, 78 AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."IdSuper" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" IN 
                                (
                                -99
                                )
                                WHERE CONVERT(date,A."DataInceput") <= CONVERT(date,GetDate()) AND CONVERT(date,GetDate()) <= CONVERT(date,A."DataSfarsit") 
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, 78 AS Rol,
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."IdSuper" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" IN 
                                (SELECT "IdUser" FROM "tblDelegari" WHERE COALESCE("IdModul",-99)=1 AND "IdDelegat"=2 AND "DataInceput" <= CONVERT(date,GetDate()) AND CONVERT(date,GetDate()) <= "DataSfarsit") ) A
                                INNER JOIN F100 B ON A.F10003 = B.F10003
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" C ON A."IdAbsenta" = C."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" M ON C."CompensareBanca" = M."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" N ON C."CompensarePlata" = N."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" Q ON A."TrimiteLa" = Q."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN F100 D ON A."Inlocuitor" = D.F10003
                                LEFT JOIN "tblSupervizori" E ON A."Rol" = E."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN (SELECT W.*, ROW_NUMBER() OVER(partition by W."IdAbs", W."IdRol", W."IdStare" ORDER BY W."IdAbs" DESC, W."IdRol" DESC, W."IdStare" DESC) "IdRow" FROM "Ptj_CereriDrepturi" W) DR ON (DR."IdAbs" = A."IdAbsenta" OR DR."IdAbs" = -13) AND (DR."IdStare" = A."IdStare" OR DR."IdStare" = -13) AND (DR."IdRol" = A."Rol" OR DR."IdRol" = -13) AND (DR."IdActiune" = 3 OR DR."IdActiune" = -13) AND DR."IdRow" <= 1
                                WHERE 1=1  AND A."Actiune" = 1 AND A."IdStare" IN (1,2) ) X

                                CASE WHEN "CampExtra12" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra12" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra12" <> ''  THEN (SELECT "Denumire" FROM "Ptj_tblAbsenteConfig" WHERE "IdAbsenta"=1 AND "IdCampExtra"=12) + '=' + "CampExtra12" + '; ' ELSE '' END +
                                CASE WHEN "CampExtra13" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra13" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra13" <> ''  THEN (SELECT "Denumire" FROM "Ptj_tblAbsenteConfig" WHERE "IdAbsenta"=1 AND "IdCampExtra"=13) + '=' + "CampExtra13" + '; ' ELSE '' END +
                                CASE WHEN "CampExtra14" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra14" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra14" <> ''  THEN (SELECT "Denumire" FROM "Ptj_tblAbsenteConfig" WHERE "IdAbsenta"=1 AND "IdCampExtra"=14) + '=' + "CampExtra14" + '; ' ELSE '' END +
                                CASE WHEN "CampExtra15" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra15" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra15" <> ''  THEN (SELECT "Denumire" FROM "Ptj_tblAbsenteConfig" WHERE "IdAbsenta"=1 AND "IdCampExtra"=15) + '=' + "CampExtra15" + '; ' ELSE '' END +
                                CASE WHEN "CampExtra16" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra16" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra16" <> ''  THEN (SELECT "Denumire" FROM "Ptj_tblAbsenteConfig" WHERE "IdAbsenta"=1 AND "IdCampExtra"=16) + '=' + "CampExtra16" + '; ' ELSE '' END +
                                CASE WHEN "CampExtra17" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra17" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra17" <> ''  THEN (SELECT "Denumire" FROM "Ptj_tblAbsenteConfig" WHERE "IdAbsenta"=1 AND "IdCampExtra"=17) + '=' + "CampExtra17" + '; ' ELSE '' END +
                                CASE WHEN "CampExtra18" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra18" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra18" <> ''  THEN (SELECT "Denumire" FROM "Ptj_tblAbsenteConfig" WHERE "IdAbsenta"=1 AND "IdCampExtra"=18) + '=' + "CampExtra18" + '; ' ELSE '' END +
                                CASE WHEN "CampExtra19" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra19" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra19" <> ''  THEN (SELECT "Denumire" FROM "Ptj_tblAbsenteConfig" WHERE "IdAbsenta"=1 AND "IdCampExtra"=19) + '=' + "CampExtra19" + '; ' ELSE '' END +
                                CASE WHEN "CampExtra20" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra20" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra20" <> ''  THEN (SELECT "Denumire" FROM "Ptj_tblAbsenteConfig" WHERE "IdAbsenta"=1 AND "IdCampExtra"=20) + '=' + "CampExtra20" + '; ' ELSE '' END + 
                                
                                CASE WHEN "OraInceput" IS NOT NULL AND "OraSfarsit" IS NOT NULL THEN 
                                SUBSTRING('00', 1, 2 - LEN(CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(HOUR, "OraInceput")))) + CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(HOUR, "OraInceput")) + ':' +
                                SUBSTRING('00', 1, 2 - LEN(CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraInceput")))) + CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraInceput")) + ' - ' +
                                SUBSTRING('00', 1, 2 - LEN(CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(HOUR, "OraSfarsit")))) + CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(HOUR, "OraSfarsit")) + ':' +
                                SUBSTRING('00', 1, 2 - LEN(CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraSfarsit")))) + CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraSfarsit")) + '; ' ELSE '' END
                                AS "DateConcatenate", DR."Valoare" AS Anulare_Valoare, DR."NrZile" AS Anulare_NrZile, COALESCE(A."CampBifa",0) AS "CampBifa"
                                FROM (SELECT A.*, 0 AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN (A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) OR B."IdCerere" IS NULL) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" = 2 AND B."IdStare" IN (1, 2, 3, 4)
                                WHERE A.F10003 = -99
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, CASE WHEN C."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN C."Id" ELSE (CASE WHEN B."IdSuper" > 0 THEN 76 ELSE C."Id" END) END AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN (A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."IdUser" = 2
                                LEFT JOIN "tblSupervizori" C ON (-1 * B."IdSuper")= C."Id"     --AND COALESCE(C."ModululCereriAbsente", 0) = 1
                                WHERE A.F10003 <> -99 
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, 78 AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."IdSuper" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" IN 
                                (
                                -99
                                )
                                WHERE CONVERT(date,A."DataInceput") <= CONVERT(date,GetDate()) AND CONVERT(date,GetDate()) <= CONVERT(date,A."DataSfarsit") 
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, 78 AS Rol,
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."IdSuper" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" IN 
                                (SELECT "IdUser" FROM "tblDelegari" WHERE COALESCE("IdModul",-99)=1 AND "IdDelegat"=2 AND "DataInceput" <= CONVERT(date,GetDate()) AND CONVERT(date,GetDate()) <= "DataSfarsit") ) A
                                INNER JOIN F100 B ON A.F10003 = B.F10003
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" C ON A."IdAbsenta" = C."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" M ON C."CompensareBanca" = M."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" N ON C."CompensarePlata" = N."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" Q ON A."TrimiteLa" = Q."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN F100 D ON A."Inlocuitor" = D.F10003
                                LEFT JOIN "tblSupervizori" E ON A."Rol" = E."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN (SELECT W.*, ROW_NUMBER() OVER(partition by W."IdAbs", W."IdRol", W."IdStare" ORDER BY W."IdAbs" DESC, W."IdRol" DESC, W."IdStare" DESC) "IdRow" FROM "Ptj_CereriDrepturi" W) DR ON (DR."IdAbs" = A."IdAbsenta" OR DR."IdAbs" = -13) AND (DR."IdStare" = A."IdStare" OR DR."IdStare" = -13) AND (DR."IdRol" = A."Rol" OR DR."IdRol" = -13) AND (DR."IdActiune" = 3 OR DR."IdActiune" = -13) AND DR."IdRow" <= 1
                                WHERE 1=1  AND A."Actiune" = 1 AND A."IdStare" IN (1,2) ) X

Eroarea:   SELECT  B."Rol", B."RolDenumire", A.F10003, A.F10008 + ' ' + A.F10009 AS "NumeComplet", 
                        X.F71804 AS "Functia", C.F00204 AS "Companie", F.F00305 AS "Subcompanie",G.F00406 AS "Filiala",H.F00507 AS "Sectie",I.F00608 AS "Departament" 
                        FROM (
                        SELECT A.F10003, 0 AS "Rol", COALESCE((SELECT COALESCE("Alias", "Denumire") FROM "tblSupervizori" WHERE "Id"=0),'Angajat') AS "RolDenumire"
                        FROM F100 A
                        WHERE A.F10003 = 2 AND (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM "Avs_Circuit" WHERE "Super1"=0) > 0
                        UNION
                        SELECT A.F10003, B."IdSuper" AS "Rol", CASE WHEN D."Alias" IS NOT NULL AND D."Alias" <> '' THEN D."Alias" ELSE D."Denumire" END AS "RolDenumire"
                        FROM F100 A
                        INNER JOIN "F100Supervizori" B ON A.F10003=B.F10003
                        INNER JOIN "Avs_Circuit" C ON B."IdSuper" = -1 * c."Super1"
                        LEFT JOIN "tblSupervizori" D ON D."Id" = B."IdSuper"
                        WHERE B."IdUser"=2
                        UNION
                        SELECT A.F10003, 76 AS "Rol", 'Fara rol' AS "RolDenumire"
                        FROM F100 A
                        INNER JOIN "Avs_Circuit" C ON C."Super1"=2
                        ) B
                        INNER JOIN F100 A ON A.F10003=B.F10003
                        LEFT JOIN F002 C ON A.F10002 = C.F00202
                        LEFT JOIN F718 X ON A.F10071=X.F71802
                        LEFT JOIN F003 F ON A.F10004 = F.F00304
                        LEFT JOIN F004 G ON A.F10005 = G.F00405
                        LEFT JOIN F005 H ON A.F10006 = H.F00506
                        LEFT JOIN F006 I ON A.F10007 = I.F00607
						WHERE A.F10025 IN (0, 999)

                                FROM (SELECT A.*, 0 AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN (A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) OR B."IdCerere" IS NULL) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" = 2 AND B."IdStare" IN (1, 2, 3, 4)
                                WHERE A.F10003 = -99
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, CASE WHEN C."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN C."Id" ELSE (CASE WHEN B."IdSuper" > 0 THEN 76 ELSE C."Id" END) END AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN (A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."IdUser" = 2
                                LEFT JOIN "tblSupervizori" C ON (-1 * B."IdSuper")= C."Id"     --AND COALESCE(C."ModululCereriAbsente", 0) = 1
                                WHERE A.F10003 <> -99 
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, 78 AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."IdSuper" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" IN 
                                (
                                -99
                                )
                                WHERE CONVERT(date,A."DataInceput") <= CONVERT(date,GetDate()) AND CONVERT(date,GetDate()) <= CONVERT(date,A."DataSfarsit") 
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, 78 AS Rol,
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."IdSuper" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" IN 
                                (SELECT "IdUser" FROM "tblDelegari" WHERE COALESCE("IdModul",-99)=1 AND "IdDelegat"=2 AND "DataInceput" <= CONVERT(date,GetDate()) AND CONVERT(date,GetDate()) <= "DataSfarsit") ) A
                                INNER JOIN F100 B ON A.F10003 = B.F10003
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" C ON A."IdAbsenta" = C."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" M ON C."CompensareBanca" = M."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" N ON C."CompensarePlata" = N."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" Q ON A."TrimiteLa" = Q."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN F100 D ON A."Inlocuitor" = D.F10003
                                LEFT JOIN "tblSupervizori" E ON A."Rol" = E."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN (SELECT W.*, ROW_NUMBER() OVER(partition by W."IdAbs", W."IdRol", W."IdStare" ORDER BY W."IdAbs" DESC, W."IdRol" DESC, W."IdStare" DESC) "IdRow" FROM "Ptj_CereriDrepturi" W) DR ON (DR."IdAbs" = A."IdAbsenta" OR DR."IdAbs" = -13) AND (DR."IdStare" = A."IdStare" OR DR."IdStare" = -13) AND (DR."IdRol" = A."Rol" OR DR."IdRol" = -13) AND (DR."IdActiune" = 3 OR DR."IdActiune" = -13) AND DR."IdRow" <= 1
                                WHERE 1=1  AND A."Actiune" = 1 AND A."IdStare" IN (1,2) ) X

                                CASE WHEN "CampExtra17" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra17" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra17" <> ''  THEN (SELECT "Denumire" FROM "Ptj_tblAbsenteConfig" WHERE "IdAbsenta"=1 AND "IdCampExtra"=17) + '=' + "CampExtra17" + '; ' ELSE '' END +

                                CASE WHEN "OraInceput" IS NOT NULL AND "OraSfarsit" IS NOT NULL THEN 
                                SUBSTRING('00', 1, 2 - LEN(CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(HOUR, "OraInceput")))) + CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(HOUR, "OraInceput")) + ':' +
                                SUBSTRING('00', 1, 2 - LEN(CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraInceput")))) + CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraInceput")) + ' - ' +
                                SUBSTRING('00', 1, 2 - LEN(CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(HOUR, "OraSfarsit")))) + CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(HOUR, "OraSfarsit")) + ':' +
                                SUBSTRING('00', 1, 2 - LEN(CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraSfarsit")))) + CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraSfarsit")) + '; ' ELSE '' END
                                AS "DateConcatenate", DR."Valoare" AS Anulare_Valoare, DR."NrZile" AS Anulare_NrZile, COALESCE(A."CampBifa",0) AS "CampBifa"
                                FROM (SELECT A.*, 0 AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN (A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) OR B."IdCerere" IS NULL) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" = 2 AND B."IdStare" IN (1, 2, 3, 4)
                                WHERE A.F10003 = -99
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, CASE WHEN C."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN C."Id" ELSE (CASE WHEN B."IdSuper" > 0 THEN 76 ELSE C."Id" END) END AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN (A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."IdUser" = 2
                                LEFT JOIN "tblSupervizori" C ON (-1 * B."IdSuper")= C."Id"     --AND COALESCE(C."ModululCereriAbsente", 0) = 1
                                WHERE A.F10003 <> -99 
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, 78 AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."IdSuper" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" IN 
                                (
                                -99
                                )
                                WHERE CONVERT(date,A."DataInceput") <= CONVERT(date,GetDate()) AND CONVERT(date,GetDate()) <= CONVERT(date,A."DataSfarsit") 
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, 78 AS Rol,
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."IdSuper" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" IN 
                                (SELECT "IdUser" FROM "tblDelegari" WHERE COALESCE("IdModul",-99)=1 AND "IdDelegat"=2 AND "DataInceput" <= CONVERT(date,GetDate()) AND CONVERT(date,GetDate()) <= "DataSfarsit") ) A
                                INNER JOIN F100 B ON A.F10003 = B.F10003
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" C ON A."IdAbsenta" = C."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" M ON C."CompensareBanca" = M."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" N ON C."CompensarePlata" = N."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" Q ON A."TrimiteLa" = Q."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN F100 D ON A."Inlocuitor" = D.F10003
                                LEFT JOIN "tblSupervizori" E ON A."Rol" = E."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN (SELECT W.*, ROW_NUMBER() OVER(partition by W."IdAbs", W."IdRol", W."IdStare" ORDER BY W."IdAbs" DESC, W."IdRol" DESC, W."IdStare" DESC) "IdRow" FROM "Ptj_CereriDrepturi" W) DR ON (DR."IdAbs" = A."IdAbsenta" OR DR."IdAbs" = -13) AND (DR."IdStare" = A."IdStare" OR DR."IdStare" = -13) AND (DR."IdRol" = A."Rol" OR DR."IdRol" = -13) AND (DR."IdActiune" = 3 OR DR."IdActiune" = -13) AND DR."IdRow" <= 1
                                WHERE 1=1  AND A."Actiune" = 1 AND A."IdStare" IN (1,2) ) X

                                CASE WHEN (A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) OR B."IdCerere" IS NULL) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" = 2 AND B."IdStare" IN (1, 2, 3, 4)
                                WHERE A.F10003 = -99
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, CASE WHEN C."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN C."Id" ELSE (CASE WHEN B."IdSuper" > 0 THEN 76 ELSE C."Id" END) END AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN (A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A

                                WHERE A.F10003 <> -99 
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, 78 AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."IdSuper" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" IN 
                                (
                                -99
                                )
                                WHERE CONVERT(date,A."DataInceput") <= CONVERT(date,GetDate()) AND CONVERT(date,GetDate()) <= CONVERT(date,A."DataSfarsit") 
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, 78 AS Rol,
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."IdSuper" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" IN 
                                (SELECT "IdUser" FROM "tblDelegari" WHERE COALESCE("IdModul",-99)=1 AND "IdDelegat"=2 AND "DataInceput" <= CONVERT(date,GetDate()) AND CONVERT(date,GetDate()) <= "DataSfarsit") ) A
                                INNER JOIN F100 B ON A.F10003 = B.F10003
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" C ON A."IdAbsenta" = C."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" M ON C."CompensareBanca" = M."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" N ON C."CompensarePlata" = N."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" Q ON A."TrimiteLa" = Q."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN F100 D ON A."Inlocuitor" = D.F10003
                                LEFT JOIN "tblSupervizori" E ON A."Rol" = E."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN (SELECT W.*, ROW_NUMBER() OVER(partition by W."IdAbs", W."IdRol", W."IdStare" ORDER BY W."IdAbs" DESC, W."IdRol" DESC, W."IdStare" DESC) "IdRow" FROM "Ptj_CereriDrepturi" W) DR ON (DR."IdAbs" = A."IdAbsenta" OR DR."IdAbs" = -13) AND (DR."IdStare" = A."IdStare" OR DR."IdStare" = -13) AND (DR."IdRol" = A."Rol" OR DR."IdRol" = -13) AND (DR."IdActiune" = 3 OR DR."IdActiune" = -13) AND DR."IdRow" <= 1
                                WHERE 1=1  AND A."Actiune" = 1 AND A."IdStare" IN (1,2) ) X

                                WHERE A.F10003 = -99
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, CASE WHEN C."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN C."Id" ELSE (CASE WHEN B."IdSuper" > 0 THEN 76 ELSE C."Id" END) END AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN (A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."IdUser" = 2
                                LEFT JOIN "tblSupervizori" C ON (-1 * B."IdSuper")= C."Id"     --AND COALESCE(C."ModululCereriAbsente", 0) = 1
                                WHERE A.F10003 <> -99 
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, 78 AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."IdSuper" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" IN

                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A

                                INNER JOIN F100 A ON b.F10003 = a.F10003

                                SUBSTRING('00', 1, 2 - LEN(CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraSfarsit")))) + CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraSfarsit")) + '; ' ELSE '' END
                                AS "DateConcatenate", DR."Valoare" AS Anulare_Valoare, DR."NrZile" AS Anulare_NrZile, COALESCE(A."CampBifa",0) AS "CampBifa"
                                FROM (SELECT A.*, 0 AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN (A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) OR B."IdCerere" IS NULL) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" = 2 AND B."IdStare" IN (1, 2, 3, 4)
                                WHERE A.F10003 = -99
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, CASE WHEN C."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN C."Id" ELSE (CASE WHEN B."IdSuper" > 0 THEN 76 ELSE C."Id" END) END AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN (A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."IdUser" = 2
                                LEFT JOIN "tblSupervizori" C ON (-1 * B."IdSuper")= C."Id"     --AND COALESCE(C."ModululCereriAbsente", 0) = 1
                                WHERE A.F10003 <> -99 
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, 78 AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."IdSuper" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" IN 
                                (
                                -99
                                )
                                WHERE CONVERT(date,A."DataInceput") <= CONVERT(date,GetDate()) AND CONVERT(date,GetDate()) <= CONVERT(date,A."DataSfarsit") 
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, 78 AS Rol,
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."IdSuper" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" IN 
                                (SELECT "IdUser" FROM "tblDelegari" WHERE COALESCE("IdModul",-99)=1 AND "IdDelegat"=2 AND "DataInceput" <= CONVERT(date,GetDate()) AND CONVERT(date,GetDate()) <= "DataSfarsit") ) A
                                INNER JOIN F100 B ON A.F10003 = B.F10003
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" C ON A."IdAbsenta" = C."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" M ON C."CompensareBanca" = M."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" N ON C."CompensarePlata" = N."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" Q ON A."TrimiteLa" = Q."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN F100 D ON A."Inlocuitor" = D.F10003
                                LEFT JOIN "tblSupervizori" E ON A."Rol" = E."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN (SELECT W.*, ROW_NUMBER() OVER(partition by W."IdAbs", W."IdRol", W."IdStare" ORDER BY W."IdAbs" DESC, W."IdRol" DESC, W."IdStare" DESC) "IdRow" FROM "Ptj_CereriDrepturi" W) DR ON (DR."IdAbs" = A."IdAbsenta" OR DR."IdAbs" = -13) AND (DR."IdStare" = A."IdStare" OR DR."IdStare" = -13) AND (DR."IdRol" = A."Rol" OR DR."IdRol" = -13) AND (DR."IdActiune" = 3 OR DR."IdActiune" = -13) AND DR."IdRow" <= 1
                                WHERE 1=1  AND A."Actiune" = 1 AND A."IdStare" IN (1,2) ) X

                                CASE WHEN (A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) OR B."IdCerere" IS NULL) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"

                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" = 2 AND B."IdStare" IN (1, 2, 3, 4)
                                WHERE A.F10003 = -99
                                UNION

                                WHERE A.F10003 <> -99 
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, 78 AS "Rol",

                                (
                                -99
                                )
                                WHERE CONVERT(date,A."DataInceput") <= CONVERT(date,GetDate()) AND CONVERT(date,GetDate()) <= CONVERT(date,A."DataSfarsit") 
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, 78 AS Rol,
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."IdSuper" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" IN 
                                (SELECT "IdUser" FROM "tblDelegari" WHERE COALESCE("IdModul",-99)=1 AND "IdDelegat"=2 AND "DataInceput" <= CONVERT(date,GetDate()) AND CONVERT(date,GetDate()) <= "DataSfarsit") ) A
                                INNER JOIN F100 B ON A.F10003 = B.F10003
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" C ON A."IdAbsenta" = C."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" M ON C."CompensareBanca" = M."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" N ON C."CompensarePlata" = N."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" Q ON A."TrimiteLa" = Q."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN F100 D ON A."Inlocuitor" = D.F10003
                                LEFT JOIN "tblSupervizori" E ON A."Rol" = E."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN (SELECT W.*, ROW_NUMBER() OVER(partition by W."IdAbs", W."IdRol", W."IdStare" ORDER BY W."IdAbs" DESC, W."IdRol" DESC, W."IdStare" DESC) "IdRow" FROM "Ptj_CereriDrepturi" W) DR ON (DR."IdAbs" = A."IdAbsenta" OR DR."IdAbs" = -13) AND (DR."IdStare" = A."IdStare" OR DR."IdStare" = -13) AND (DR."IdRol" = A."Rol" OR DR."IdRol" = -13) AND (DR."IdActiune" = 3 OR DR."IdActiune" = -13) AND DR."IdRow" <= 1
                                WHERE 1=1  AND A."Actiune" = 1 AND A."IdStare" IN (1,2) ) X

                                WHERE A.F10003 <> -99 
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, 78 AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."IdSuper" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" IN 
                                (
                                -99
                                )
                                WHERE CONVERT(date,A."DataInceput") <= CONVERT(date,GetDate()) AND CONVERT(date,GetDate()) <= CONVERT(date,A."DataSfarsit") 
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, 78 AS Rol,
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."IdSuper" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" IN 
                                (SELECT "IdUser" FROM "tblDelegari" WHERE COALESCE("IdModul",-99)=1 AND "IdDelegat"=2 AND "DataInceput" <= CONVERT(date,GetDate()) AND CONVERT(date,GetDate()) <= "DataSfarsit") ) A
                                INNER JOIN F100 B ON A.F10003 = B.F10003
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" C ON A."IdAbsenta" = C."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" M ON C."CompensareBanca" = M."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" N ON C."CompensarePlata" = N."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" Q ON A."TrimiteLa" = Q."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN F100 D ON A."Inlocuitor" = D.F10003
                                LEFT JOIN "tblSupervizori" E ON A."Rol" = E."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN (SELECT W.*, ROW_NUMBER() OVER(partition by W."IdAbs", W."IdRol", W."IdStare" ORDER BY W."IdAbs" DESC, W."IdRol" DESC, W."IdStare" DESC) "IdRow" FROM "Ptj_CereriDrepturi" W) DR ON (DR."IdAbs" = A."IdAbsenta" OR DR."IdAbs" = -13) AND (DR."IdStare" = A."IdStare" OR DR."IdStare" = -13) AND (DR."IdRol" = A."Rol" OR DR."IdRol" = -13) AND (DR."IdActiune" = 3 OR DR."IdActiune" = -13) AND DR."IdRow" <= 1
                                WHERE 1=1  AND A."Actiune" = 1 AND A."IdStare" IN (1,2) ) X

                                SUBSTRING('00', 1, 2 - LEN(CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraInceput")))) + CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraInceput")) + ' - ' +
                                SUBSTRING('00', 1, 2 - LEN(CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(HOUR, "OraSfarsit")))) + CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(HOUR, "OraSfarsit")) + ':' +
                                SUBSTRING('00', 1, 2 - LEN(CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraSfarsit")))) + CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraSfarsit")) + '; ' ELSE '' END
                                AS "DateConcatenate", DR."Valoare" AS Anulare_Valoare, DR."NrZile" AS Anulare_NrZile, COALESCE(A."CampBifa",0) AS "CampBifa"
                                FROM (SELECT A.*, 0 AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN (A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) OR B."IdCerere" IS NULL) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" = 2 AND B."IdStare" IN (1, 2, 3, 4)
                                WHERE A.F10003 = -99
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, CASE WHEN C."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN C."Id" ELSE (CASE WHEN B."IdSuper" > 0 THEN 76 ELSE C."Id" END) END AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN (A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."IdUser" = 2
                                LEFT JOIN "tblSupervizori" C ON (-1 * B."IdSuper")= C."Id"     --AND COALESCE(C."ModululCereriAbsente", 0) = 1
                                WHERE A.F10003 <> -99 
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, 78 AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."IdSuper" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" IN 
                                (
                                -99
                                )
                                WHERE CONVERT(date,A."DataInceput") <= CONVERT(date,GetDate()) AND CONVERT(date,GetDate()) <= CONVERT(date,A."DataSfarsit") 
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, 78 AS Rol,
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."IdSuper" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" IN 
                                (SELECT "IdUser" FROM "tblDelegari" WHERE COALESCE("IdModul",-99)=1 AND "IdDelegat"=2 AND "DataInceput" <= CONVERT(date,GetDate()) AND CONVERT(date,GetDate()) <= "DataSfarsit") ) A
                                INNER JOIN F100 B ON A.F10003 = B.F10003
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" C ON A."IdAbsenta" = C."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" M ON C."CompensareBanca" = M."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" N ON C."CompensarePlata" = N."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" Q ON A."TrimiteLa" = Q."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN F100 D ON A."Inlocuitor" = D.F10003
                                LEFT JOIN "tblSupervizori" E ON A."Rol" = E."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN (SELECT W.*, ROW_NUMBER() OVER(partition by W."IdAbs", W."IdRol", W."IdStare" ORDER BY W."IdAbs" DESC, W."IdRol" DESC, W."IdStare" DESC) "IdRow" FROM "Ptj_CereriDrepturi" W) DR ON (DR."IdAbs" = A."IdAbsenta" OR DR."IdAbs" = -13) AND (DR."IdStare" = A."IdStare" OR DR."IdStare" = -13) AND (DR."IdRol" = A."Rol" OR DR."IdRol" = -13) AND (DR."IdActiune" = 3 OR DR."IdActiune" = -13) AND DR."IdRow" <= 1
                                WHERE 1=1  AND A."Actiune" = 1 AND A."IdStare" IN (1,2) ) X

                                CASE WHEN "CampExtra17" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra17" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra17" <> ''  THEN (SELECT "Denumire" FROM "Ptj_tblAbsenteConfig" WHERE "IdAbsenta"=1 AND "IdCampExtra"=17) + '=' + "CampExtra17" + '; ' ELSE '' END +
                                CASE WHEN "CampExtra18" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra18" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra18" <> ''  THEN (SELECT "Denumire" FROM "Ptj_tblAbsenteConfig" WHERE "IdAbsenta"=1 AND "IdCampExtra"=18) + '=' + "CampExtra18" + '; ' ELSE '' END +
                                CASE WHEN "CampExtra19" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra19" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra19" <> ''  THEN (SELECT "Denumire" FROM "Ptj_tblAbsenteConfig" WHERE "IdAbsenta"=1 AND "IdCampExtra"=19) + '=' + "CampExtra19" + '; ' ELSE '' END +
                                CASE WHEN "CampExtra20" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra20" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra20" <> ''  THEN (SELECT "Denumire" FROM "Ptj_tblAbsenteConfig" WHERE "IdAbsenta"=1 AND "IdCampExtra"=20) + '=' + "CampExtra20" + '; ' ELSE '' END + 
                                
                                CASE WHEN "OraInceput" IS NOT NULL AND "OraSfarsit" IS NOT NULL THEN 
                                SUBSTRING('00', 1, 2 - LEN(CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(HOUR, "OraInceput")))) + CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(HOUR, "OraInceput")) + ':' +
                                SUBSTRING('00', 1, 2 - LEN(CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraInceput")))) + CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraInceput")) + ' - ' +
                                SUBSTRING('00', 1, 2 - LEN(CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(HOUR, "OraSfarsit")))) + CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(HOUR, "OraSfarsit")) + ':' +
                                SUBSTRING('00', 1, 2 - LEN(CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraSfarsit")))) + CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraSfarsit")) + '; ' ELSE '' END
                                AS "DateConcatenate", DR."Valoare" AS Anulare_Valoare, DR."NrZile" AS Anulare_NrZile, COALESCE(A."CampBifa",0) AS "CampBifa"
                                FROM (SELECT A.*, 0 AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN (A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) OR B."IdCerere" IS NULL) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" = 2 AND B."IdStare" IN (1, 2, 3, 4)
                                WHERE A.F10003 = -99
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, CASE WHEN C."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN C."Id" ELSE (CASE WHEN B."IdSuper" > 0 THEN 76 ELSE C."Id" END) END AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN (A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."IdUser" = 2
                                LEFT JOIN "tblSupervizori" C ON (-1 * B."IdSuper")= C."Id"     --AND COALESCE(C."ModululCereriAbsente", 0) = 1
                                WHERE A.F10003 <> -99 
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, 78 AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."IdSuper" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" IN 
                                (
                                -99
                                )
                                WHERE CONVERT(date,A."DataInceput") <= CONVERT(date,GetDate()) AND CONVERT(date,GetDate()) <= CONVERT(date,A."DataSfarsit") 
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, 78 AS Rol,
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."IdSuper" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" IN 
                                (SELECT "IdUser" FROM "tblDelegari" WHERE COALESCE("IdModul",-99)=1 AND "IdDelegat"=2 AND "DataInceput" <= CONVERT(date,GetDate()) AND CONVERT(date,GetDate()) <= "DataSfarsit") ) A
                                INNER JOIN F100 B ON A.F10003 = B.F10003
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" C ON A."IdAbsenta" = C."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" M ON C."CompensareBanca" = M."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" N ON C."CompensarePlata" = N."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" Q ON A."TrimiteLa" = Q."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN F100 D ON A."Inlocuitor" = D.F10003
                                LEFT JOIN "tblSupervizori" E ON A."Rol" = E."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN (SELECT W.*, ROW_NUMBER() OVER(partition by W."IdAbs", W."IdRol", W."IdStare" ORDER BY W."IdAbs" DESC, W."IdRol" DESC, W."IdStare" DESC) "IdRow" FROM "Ptj_CereriDrepturi" W) DR ON (DR."IdAbs" = A."IdAbsenta" OR DR."IdAbs" = -13) AND (DR."IdStare" = A."IdStare" OR DR."IdStare" = -13) AND (DR."IdRol" = A."Rol" OR DR."IdRol" = -13) AND (DR."IdActiune" = 3 OR DR."IdActiune" = -13) AND DR."IdRow" <= 1
                                WHERE 1=1  AND A."Actiune" = 1 AND A."IdStare" IN (1,2) ) X

                                CASE WHEN "CampExtra10" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra10" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra10" <> ''  THEN (SELECT "Denumire" FROM "Ptj_tblAbsenteConfig" WHERE "IdAbsenta"=1 AND "IdCampExtra"=10) + '=' + "CampExtra10" + '; ' ELSE '' END +
                                CASE WHEN "CampExtra11" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra11" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra11" <> ''  THEN (SELECT "Denumire" FROM "Ptj_tblAbsenteConfig" WHERE "IdAbsenta"=1 AND "IdCampExtra"=11) + '=' + "CampExtra11" + '; ' ELSE '' END +
                                CASE WHEN "CampExtra12" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra12" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra12" <> ''  THEN (SELECT "Denumire" FROM "Ptj_tblAbsenteConfig" WHERE "IdAbsenta"=1 AND "IdCampExtra"=12) + '=' + "CampExtra12" + '; ' ELSE '' END +
                                CASE WHEN "CampExtra13" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra13" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra13" <> ''  THEN (SELECT "Denumire" FROM "Ptj_tblAbsenteConfig" WHERE "IdAbsenta"=1 AND "IdCampExtra"=13) + '=' + "CampExtra13" + '; ' ELSE '' END +
                                CASE WHEN "CampExtra14" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra14" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra14" <> ''  THEN (SELECT "Denumire" FROM "Ptj_tblAbsenteConfig" WHERE "IdAbsenta"=1 AND "IdCampExtra"=14) + '=' + "CampExtra14" + '; ' ELSE '' END +
                                CASE WHEN "CampExtra15" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra15" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra15" <> ''  THEN (SELECT "Denumire" FROM "Ptj_tblAbsenteConfig" WHERE "IdAbsenta"=1 AND "IdCampExtra"=15) + '=' + "CampExtra15" + '; ' ELSE '' END +
                                CASE WHEN "CampExtra16" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra16" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra16" <> ''  THEN (SELECT "Denumire" FROM "Ptj_tblAbsenteConfig" WHERE "IdAbsenta"=1 AND "IdCampExtra"=16) + '=' + "CampExtra16" + '; ' ELSE '' END +
                                CASE WHEN "CampExtra17" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra17" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra17" <> ''  THEN (SELECT "Denumire" FROM "Ptj_tblAbsenteConfig" WHERE "IdAbsenta"=1 AND "IdCampExtra"=17) + '=' + "CampExtra17" + '; ' ELSE '' END +
                                CASE WHEN "CampExtra18" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra18" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra18" <> ''  THEN (SELECT "Denumire" FROM "Ptj_tblAbsenteConfig" WHERE "IdAbsenta"=1 AND "IdCampExtra"=18) + '=' + "CampExtra18" + '; ' ELSE '' END +
                                CASE WHEN "CampExtra19" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra19" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra19" <> ''  THEN (SELECT "Denumire" FROM "Ptj_tblAbsenteConfig" WHERE "IdAbsenta"=1 AND "IdCampExtra"=19) + '=' + "CampExtra19" + '; ' ELSE '' END +
                                CASE WHEN "CampExtra20" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra20" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra20" <> ''  THEN (SELECT "Denumire" FROM "Ptj_tblAbsenteConfig" WHERE "IdAbsenta"=1 AND "IdCampExtra"=20) + '=' + "CampExtra20" + '; ' ELSE '' END + 
                                
                                CASE WHEN "OraInceput" IS NOT NULL AND "OraSfarsit" IS NOT NULL THEN 
                                SUBSTRING('00', 1, 2 - LEN(CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(HOUR, "OraInceput")))) + CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(HOUR, "OraInceput")) + ':' +
                                SUBSTRING('00', 1, 2 - LEN(CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraInceput")))) + CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraInceput")) + ' - ' +
                                SUBSTRING('00', 1, 2 - LEN(CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(HOUR, "OraSfarsit")))) + CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(HOUR, "OraSfarsit")) + ':' +
                                SUBSTRING('00', 1, 2 - LEN(CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraSfarsit")))) + CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraSfarsit")) + '; ' ELSE '' END
                                AS "DateConcatenate", DR."Valoare" AS Anulare_Valoare, DR."NrZile" AS Anulare_NrZile, COALESCE(A."CampBifa",0) AS "CampBifa"
                                FROM (SELECT A.*, 0 AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN (A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) OR B."IdCerere" IS NULL) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" = 2 AND B."IdStare" IN (1, 2, 3, 4)
                                WHERE A.F10003 = -99
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, CASE WHEN C."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN C."Id" ELSE (CASE WHEN B."IdSuper" > 0 THEN 76 ELSE C."Id" END) END AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN (A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."IdUser" = 2
                                LEFT JOIN "tblSupervizori" C ON (-1 * B."IdSuper")= C."Id"     --AND COALESCE(C."ModululCereriAbsente", 0) = 1
                                WHERE A.F10003 <> -99 
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, 78 AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."IdSuper" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" IN 
                                (
                                -99
                                )
                                WHERE CONVERT(date,A."DataInceput") <= CONVERT(date,GetDate()) AND CONVERT(date,GetDate()) <= CONVERT(date,A."DataSfarsit") 
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, 78 AS Rol,
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."IdSuper" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" IN 
                                (SELECT "IdUser" FROM "tblDelegari" WHERE COALESCE("IdModul",-99)=1 AND "IdDelegat"=2 AND "DataInceput" <= CONVERT(date,GetDate()) AND CONVERT(date,GetDate()) <= "DataSfarsit") ) A
                                INNER JOIN F100 B ON A.F10003 = B.F10003
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" C ON A."IdAbsenta" = C."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" M ON C."CompensareBanca" = M."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" N ON C."CompensarePlata" = N."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" Q ON A."TrimiteLa" = Q."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN F100 D ON A."Inlocuitor" = D.F10003
                                LEFT JOIN "tblSupervizori" E ON A."Rol" = E."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN (SELECT W.*, ROW_NUMBER() OVER(partition by W."IdAbs", W."IdRol", W."IdStare" ORDER BY W."IdAbs" DESC, W."IdRol" DESC, W."IdStare" DESC) "IdRow" FROM "Ptj_CereriDrepturi" W) DR ON (DR."IdAbs" = A."IdAbsenta" OR DR."IdAbs" = -13) AND (DR."IdStare" = A."IdStare" OR DR."IdStare" = -13) AND (DR."IdRol" = A."Rol" OR DR."IdRol" = -13) AND (DR."IdActiune" = 3 OR DR."IdActiune" = -13) AND DR."IdRow" <= 1
                                WHERE 1=1  AND A."Actiune" = 1 AND A."IdStare" IN (1,2) ) X

                                SUBSTRING('00', 1, 2 - LEN(CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(HOUR, "OraInceput")))) + CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(HOUR, "OraInceput")) + ':' +
                                SUBSTRING('00', 1, 2 - LEN(CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraInceput")))) + CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraInceput")) + ' - ' +
                                SUBSTRING('00', 1, 2 - LEN(CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(HOUR, "OraSfarsit")))) + CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(HOUR, "OraSfarsit")) + ':' +
                                SUBSTRING('00', 1, 2 - LEN(CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraSfarsit")))) + CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraSfarsit")) + '; ' ELSE '' END
                                AS "DateConcatenate", DR."Valoare" AS Anulare_Valoare, DR."NrZile" AS Anulare_NrZile, COALESCE(A."CampBifa",0) AS "CampBifa"
                                FROM (SELECT A.*, 0 AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN (A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) OR B."IdCerere" IS NULL) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" = 2 AND B."IdStare" IN (1, 2, 3, 4)
                                WHERE A.F10003 = -99
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, CASE WHEN C."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN C."Id" ELSE (CASE WHEN B."IdSuper" > 0 THEN 76 ELSE C."Id" END) END AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN (A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."IdUser" = 2
                                LEFT JOIN "tblSupervizori" C ON (-1 * B."IdSuper")= C."Id"     --AND COALESCE(C."ModululCereriAbsente", 0) = 1
                                WHERE A.F10003 <> -99 
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, 78 AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."IdSuper" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" IN 
                                (
                                -99
                                )
                                WHERE CONVERT(date,A."DataInceput") <= CONVERT(date,GetDate()) AND CONVERT(date,GetDate()) <= CONVERT(date,A."DataSfarsit") 
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, 78 AS Rol,
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."IdSuper" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" IN 
                                (SELECT "IdUser" FROM "tblDelegari" WHERE COALESCE("IdModul",-99)=1 AND "IdDelegat"=2 AND "DataInceput" <= CONVERT(date,GetDate()) AND CONVERT(date,GetDate()) <= "DataSfarsit") ) A
                                INNER JOIN F100 B ON A.F10003 = B.F10003
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" C ON A."IdAbsenta" = C."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" M ON C."CompensareBanca" = M."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" N ON C."CompensarePlata" = N."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" Q ON A."TrimiteLa" = Q."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN F100 D ON A."Inlocuitor" = D.F10003
                                LEFT JOIN "tblSupervizori" E ON A."Rol" = E."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN (SELECT W.*, ROW_NUMBER() OVER(partition by W."IdAbs", W."IdRol", W."IdStare" ORDER BY W."IdAbs" DESC, W."IdRol" DESC, W."IdStare" DESC) "IdRow" FROM "Ptj_CereriDrepturi" W) DR ON (DR."IdAbs" = A."IdAbsenta" OR DR."IdAbs" = -13) AND (DR."IdStare" = A."IdStare" OR DR."IdStare" = -13) AND (DR."IdRol" = A."Rol" OR DR."IdRol" = -13) AND (DR."IdActiune" = 3 OR DR."IdActiune" = -13) AND DR."IdRow" <= 1
                                WHERE 1=1  AND A."Actiune" = 1 AND A."IdStare" IN (1,2) ) X

                                CASE WHEN "OraInceput" IS NOT NULL AND "OraSfarsit" IS NOT NULL THEN 
                                SUBSTRING('00', 1, 2 - LEN(CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(HOUR, "OraInceput")))) + CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(HOUR, "OraInceput")) + ':' +
                                SUBSTRING('00', 1, 2 - LEN(CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraInceput")))) + CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraInceput")) + ' - ' +
                                SUBSTRING('00', 1, 2 - LEN(CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(HOUR, "OraSfarsit")))) + CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(HOUR, "OraSfarsit")) + ':' +
                                SUBSTRING('00', 1, 2 - LEN(CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraSfarsit")))) + CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraSfarsit")) + '; ' ELSE '' END
                                AS "DateConcatenate", DR."Valoare" AS Anulare_Valoare, DR."NrZile" AS Anulare_NrZile, COALESCE(A."CampBifa",0) AS "CampBifa"
                                FROM (SELECT A.*, 0 AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN (A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) OR B."IdCerere" IS NULL) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" = 2 AND B."IdStare" IN (1, 2, 3, 4)
                                WHERE A.F10003 = -99
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, CASE WHEN C."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN C."Id" ELSE (CASE WHEN B."IdSuper" > 0 THEN 76 ELSE C."Id" END) END AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN (A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."IdUser" = 2
                                LEFT JOIN "tblSupervizori" C ON (-1 * B."IdSuper")= C."Id"     --AND COALESCE(C."ModululCereriAbsente", 0) = 1
                                WHERE A.F10003 <> -99 
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, 78 AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."IdSuper" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" IN 
                                (
                                -99
                                )
                                WHERE CONVERT(date,A."DataInceput") <= CONVERT(date,GetDate()) AND CONVERT(date,GetDate()) <= CONVERT(date,A."DataSfarsit") 
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, 78 AS Rol,
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."IdSuper" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" IN 
                                (SELECT "IdUser" FROM "tblDelegari" WHERE COALESCE("IdModul",-99)=1 AND "IdDelegat"=2 AND "DataInceput" <= CONVERT(date,GetDate()) AND CONVERT(date,GetDate()) <= "DataSfarsit") ) A
                                INNER JOIN F100 B ON A.F10003 = B.F10003
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" C ON A."IdAbsenta" = C."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" M ON C."CompensareBanca" = M."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" N ON C."CompensarePlata" = N."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" Q ON A."TrimiteLa" = Q."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN F100 D ON A."Inlocuitor" = D.F10003
                                LEFT JOIN "tblSupervizori" E ON A."Rol" = E."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN (SELECT W.*, ROW_NUMBER() OVER(partition by W."IdAbs", W."IdRol", W."IdStare" ORDER BY W."IdAbs" DESC, W."IdRol" DESC, W."IdStare" DESC) "IdRow" FROM "Ptj_CereriDrepturi" W) DR ON (DR."IdAbs" = A."IdAbsenta" OR DR."IdAbs" = -13) AND (DR."IdStare" = A."IdStare" OR DR."IdStare" = -13) AND (DR."IdRol" = A."Rol" OR DR."IdRol" = -13) AND (DR."IdActiune" = 3 OR DR."IdActiune" = -13) AND DR."IdRow" <= 1
                                WHERE 1=1  AND A."Actiune" = 1 AND A."IdStare" IN (1,2) ) X

                                UNION

                                WHERE 1=1 ) X GROUP BY "Rol", "RolDenumire"
                            UNION 
                            SELECT -1 AS "Rol", 'Toate' AS "RolDenumire", 0 AS "Ordin"   ) Y WHERE Y."Rol" IS NOT NULL ORDER BY "Ordin"

                               INNER JOIN "F100Supervizori" B ON A.F10003 = B.F10003 AND B."IdSuper" IN (3) AND B."IdUser" = 6) A
                                INNER JOIN F100 B ON A.F10003 = B.F10003
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" C ON A."IdAbsenta" = C."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" M ON C."CompensareBanca" = M."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" N ON C."CompensarePlata" = N."Id"

                                LEFT JOIN "tblSupervizori" E ON A."Rol" = E."Id"

                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN (A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."IdUser" = 6

                                UNION

                                SUBSTRING('00', 1, 2 - LEN(CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraInceput")))) + CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraInceput")) + ' - ' +
                                SUBSTRING('00', 1, 2 - LEN(CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(HOUR, "OraSfarsit")))) + CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(HOUR, "OraSfarsit")) + ':' +
                                SUBSTRING('00', 1, 2 - LEN(CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraSfarsit")))) + CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraSfarsit")) + '; ' ELSE '' END
                                AS "DateConcatenate", DR."Valoare" AS Anulare_Valoare, DR."NrZile" AS Anulare_NrZile, COALESCE(A."CampBifa",0) AS "CampBifa"

                                CASE WHEN (A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) OR B."IdCerere" IS NULL) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" = 6 AND B."IdStare" IN (1, 2, 3)
                                WHERE A.F10003 = -99
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, CASE WHEN C."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN C."Id" ELSE (CASE WHEN B."IdSuper" > 0 THEN 76 ELSE C."Id" END) END AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN (A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."IdUser" = 6
                                LEFT JOIN "tblSupervizori" C ON (-1 * B."IdSuper")= C."Id"     --AND COALESCE(C."ModululCereriAbsente", 0) = 1
                                WHERE A.F10003 <> -99  AND A."IdStare" IN (1, 2, 3) 
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, 78 AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."IdSuper" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" IN 
                                (
                                SELECT Y.F70102 FROM "Ptj_Cereri" X
                                INNER JOIN USERS Y ON X.F10003=Y.F10003
                                WHERE X."IdStare"=3 AND X."Inlocuitor" = -99
                                AND CONVERT(date,X."DataInceput") <= CONVERT(date,GetDate()) AND CONVERT(date,GetDate()) <= CONVERT(date,X."DataSfarsit")
                                )
                                WHERE CONVERT(date,A."DataInceput") <= CONVERT(date,GetDate()) AND CONVERT(date,GetDate()) <= CONVERT(date,A."DataSfarsit")  AND A."IdStare" IN (1, 2, 3) 
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, 78 AS Rol,
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."IdSuper" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" IN 
                                (SELECT "IdUser" FROM "tblDelegari" WHERE COALESCE("IdModul",-99)=1 AND "IdDelegat"=6 AND "DataInceput" <= CONVERT(date,GetDate()) AND CONVERT(date,GetDate()) <= "DataSfarsit")  AND A."IdStare" IN (1, 2, 3) ) A
                                INNER JOIN F100 B ON A.F10003 = B.F10003
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" C ON A."IdAbsenta" = C."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" M ON C."CompensareBanca" = M."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" N ON C."CompensarePlata" = N."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" Q ON A."TrimiteLa" = Q."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN F100 D ON A."Inlocuitor" = D.F10003
                                LEFT JOIN "tblSupervizori" E ON A."Rol" = E."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN (SELECT W.*, ROW_NUMBER() OVER(partition by W."IdAbs", W."IdRol", W."IdStare" ORDER BY W."IdAbs" DESC, W."IdRol" DESC, W."IdStare" DESC) "IdRow" FROM "Ptj_CereriDrepturi" W) DR ON (DR."IdAbs" = A."IdAbsenta" OR DR."IdAbs" = -13) AND (DR."IdStare" = A."IdStare" OR DR."IdStare" = -13) AND (DR."IdRol" = A."Rol" OR DR."IdRol" = -13) AND (DR."IdActiune" = 3 OR DR."IdActiune" = -13) AND DR."IdRow" <= 1
                                WHERE 1=1   AND A."Actiune"=1  AND A."DataInceput" <= CONVERT(date,'2100-01-01') AND CONVERT(date,'2019-07-01') <= A."DataSfarsit"  ORDER BY A.TIME DESC

                                WHERE 1=1   AND A."Actiune"=1  AND A."DataInceput" <= CONVERT(date,'2100-01-01') AND CONVERT(date,'2019-10-01') <= A."DataSfarsit"  ORDER BY A.TIME DESC

                                (SELECT "IdUser" FROM "tblDelegari" WHERE COALESCE("IdModul",-99)=1 AND "IdDelegat"=5 AND "DataInceput" <= CONVERT(date,GetDate()) AND CONVERT(date,GetDate()) <= "DataSfarsit") ) A

                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" C ON A."IdAbsenta" = C."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" M ON C."CompensareBanca" = M."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" N ON C."CompensarePlata" = N."Id"

                                WHERE 1=1 ) X GROUP BY "Rol", "RolDenumire"

                                CASE WHEN "CampExtra16" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra16" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra16" <> ''  THEN (SELECT "Denumire" FROM "Ptj_tblAbsenteConfig" WHERE "IdAbsenta"=1 AND "IdCampExtra"=16) + '=' + "CampExtra16" + '; ' ELSE '' END +
                                CASE WHEN "CampExtra17" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra17" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra17" <> ''  THEN (SELECT "Denumire" FROM "Ptj_tblAbsenteConfig" WHERE "IdAbsenta"=1 AND "IdCampExtra"=17) + '=' + "CampExtra17" + '; ' ELSE '' END +
                                CASE WHEN "CampExtra18" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra18" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra18" <> ''  THEN (SELECT "Denumire" FROM "Ptj_tblAbsenteConfig" WHERE "IdAbsenta"=1 AND "IdCampExtra"=18) + '=' + "CampExtra18" + '; ' ELSE '' END +
                                CASE WHEN "CampExtra19" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra19" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra19" <> ''  THEN (SELECT "Denumire" FROM "Ptj_tblAbsenteConfig" WHERE "IdAbsenta"=1 AND "IdCampExtra"=19) + '=' + "CampExtra19" + '; ' ELSE '' END +
                                CASE WHEN "CampExtra20" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra20" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra20" <> ''  THEN (SELECT "Denumire" FROM "Ptj_tblAbsenteConfig" WHERE "IdAbsenta"=1 AND "IdCampExtra"=20) + '=' + "CampExtra20" + '; ' ELSE '' END + 
                                
                                CASE WHEN "OraInceput" IS NOT NULL AND "OraSfarsit" IS NOT NULL THEN 
                                SUBSTRING('00', 1, 2 - LEN(CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(HOUR, "OraInceput")))) + CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(HOUR, "OraInceput")) + ':' +
                                SUBSTRING('00', 1, 2 - LEN(CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraInceput")))) + CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraInceput")) + ' - ' +
                                SUBSTRING('00', 1, 2 - LEN(CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(HOUR, "OraSfarsit")))) + CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(HOUR, "OraSfarsit")) + ':' +
                                SUBSTRING('00', 1, 2 - LEN(CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraSfarsit")))) + CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraSfarsit")) + '; ' ELSE '' END
                                AS "DateConcatenate", DR."Valoare" AS Anulare_Valoare, DR."NrZile" AS Anulare_NrZile, COALESCE(A."CampBifa",0) AS "CampBifa"
                                FROM (SELECT A.*, 0 AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN (A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) OR B."IdCerere" IS NULL) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" = 2 AND B."IdStare" IN (1, 2, 3, 4)
                                WHERE A.F10003 = -99
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, CASE WHEN C."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN C."Id" ELSE (CASE WHEN B."IdSuper" > 0 THEN 76 ELSE C."Id" END) END AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN (A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."IdUser" = 2
                                LEFT JOIN "tblSupervizori" C ON (-1 * B."IdSuper")= C."Id"     --AND COALESCE(C."ModululCereriAbsente", 0) = 1
                                WHERE A.F10003 <> -99 
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, 78 AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."IdSuper" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" IN 
                                (
                                -99
                                )
                                WHERE CONVERT(date,A."DataInceput") <= CONVERT(date,GetDate()) AND CONVERT(date,GetDate()) <= CONVERT(date,A."DataSfarsit") 
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, 78 AS Rol,
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."IdSuper" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" IN 
                                (SELECT "IdUser" FROM "tblDelegari" WHERE COALESCE("IdModul",-99)=1 AND "IdDelegat"=2 AND "DataInceput" <= CONVERT(date,GetDate()) AND CONVERT(date,GetDate()) <= "DataSfarsit") ) A
                                INNER JOIN F100 B ON A.F10003 = B.F10003
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" C ON A."IdAbsenta" = C."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" M ON C."CompensareBanca" = M."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" N ON C."CompensarePlata" = N."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" Q ON A."TrimiteLa" = Q."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN F100 D ON A."Inlocuitor" = D.F10003
                                LEFT JOIN "tblSupervizori" E ON A."Rol" = E."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN (SELECT W.*, ROW_NUMBER() OVER(partition by W."IdAbs", W."IdRol", W."IdStare" ORDER BY W."IdAbs" DESC, W."IdRol" DESC, W."IdStare" DESC) "IdRow" FROM "Ptj_CereriDrepturi" W) DR ON (DR."IdAbs" = A."IdAbsenta" OR DR."IdAbs" = -13) AND (DR."IdStare" = A."IdStare" OR DR."IdStare" = -13) AND (DR."IdRol" = A."Rol" OR DR."IdRol" = -13) AND (DR."IdActiune" = 3 OR DR."IdActiune" = -13) AND DR."IdRow" <= 1
                                WHERE 1=1   AND A."DataInceput" <= CONVERT(date,'2100-01-01') AND CONVERT(date,'2019-09-04') <= A."DataSfarsit"  ORDER BY A.TIME DESC

                                SUBSTRING('00', 1, 2 - LEN(CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraInceput")))) + CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraInceput")) + ' - ' +

                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A

                                UNION

                                )

                                INNER JOIN USERS Y ON X.F10003=Y.F10003
                                WHERE X."IdStare"=3 AND X."Inlocuitor" = 2648

                                WHERE 1=1 ) X GROUP BY "Rol", "RolDenumire"

                                CASE WHEN (A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) OR B."IdCerere" IS NULL) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"

                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" = 7 AND B."IdStare" IN (1, 2, 3, 4)
                                WHERE A.F10003 = 2648
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, CASE WHEN C."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN C."Id" ELSE (CASE WHEN B."IdSuper" > 0 THEN 76 ELSE C."Id" END) END AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN (A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."IdUser" = 7

                                WHERE A.F10003 <> 2648 
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, 78 AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
